{"tid":189941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己老婆自己「造」，AI工程師娶機械人為妻","createTime":"2017-04-06T19:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T03:51:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa07cf6ddf3f6cf79fe993ff39b8a566e709cf6b","tid":189941,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:22:50.000Z","msg":"By Presslogic on 05 Apr 2017<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Robot-wife-FB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FRobot-wife-FB.png&h=4752e47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n找不到老婆就自己設計一個出來吧！一名31歲中國AI工程師鄭佳佳日前宣布，已經娶了由自己一手設計的機械女子為妻，更在自己創辦的公司開一個發言人職位給「老婆」，表示希望將來每個家庭都能擁有機械人。<br />\n<br />\nWeibo<br />\nPhoto by Weibo<br />\n鄭佳佳與「鄭太」的婚禮走傳統路線，新娘頭披紅色面紗，驟眼看根本難以知悉「她」其實是機械人。鄭佳佳的母親和朋友亦參加了他和「鄭太」的婚禮儀式，為他們送上祝福。<br />\n<br />\nWeibo<br />\nPhoto by Weibo<br />\n「鄭太」的名字叫瑩瑩，能夠用簡單句子對話，識別漢字及圖像。鄭佳佳已計劃為瑩瑩升級，賦予她走路及打理家務的能力。他表示希望閒時帶她到小鎮上散步，和她一起慢慢變老。<br />\n<br />\nPEAR VIDEO <br />\nPhoto by PEAR VIDEO<br />\n鄭佳佳曾在中國電信巨頭華為工作，專門研發AI及機械人。現時在杭州創辦了一間名為「腦物科學」的初企，推動AI及神經網絡技術，瑩瑩在結婚後榮升「老闆娘」，成為公司發言人。鄭佳佳揚言，未來要打造現實的機械人女友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/05/article/23572/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2Farticle%2F23572%2F&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=98419304\" target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/05/article/23572/</a>"},{"pid":"1637b8b6fa54c9981d96abef8cd1387fe1a138ea","tid":189941,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:40:23.000Z","msg":"佢老婆會唔會爆炸？"},{"pid":"17500c2e5a6a362e1521728466f7b910f956161e","tid":189941,"uid":3061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T20:46:50.000Z","msg":"Chobits <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi